==Russian==
===Noun===
'''лес''' (les) ''m'', леса (lesá) ''pl''

# [[forest]], [[woods]]
#:леса́ (lesá) ''pl'' — ''[[woodland]], [[forests]]''
#:[[девственный]] лес (dévstvennyj) — ''[[virgin]] [[forest]]'', ''[[primeval]] [[forest]]''
#:[[заповедный]] лес means:
#::[[заповедник]] - ''[[protection]] [[forest]]''
#::{{poetic}} [[тайный]] лес, [[священный]] лес, [[божий]] лес — ''[[sacred]] [[forest]]'', the forest that nobody may go into
#:[[корабельный]] лес (korabélnyj) — ''[[ship]] [[timber]]''
#:[[лиственный]] лес (lístvennyj) — ''[[leaf-bearing]] [[forest]]''
#:[[смешанный]] лес (sméšannyj) — ''[[mixed]] [[forest]]''
#:[[тропический]] лес (tropíčeskij) — ''[[rainforest]]''
#:[[хвойный]] лес (khvójnyj) — ''[[coniferous]] [[forest]]''
#:[[чаща]] леса — ''[[thicket]]'', ''the [[depths]] of [[forest]]''
#:[[шум]] леса — ''[[murmur]] of the [[forest]]''
#:[[как]] [[в]] лесу (kak v lesú) ''(saying)'' — ''at [[sea]], [[lost]], [[disoriented]]''
#:кто в лес, кто по дрова ''(proverb)'' &mdash; ''(to be) at sixes and sevens'' (''literal'': someone goes to forest, someone goes for firewood)
#:лес рубят &mdash; щепки летят ''(proverb)'' &mdash; ''you can't make omelettes without breaking eggs'' (''literal'': when wood is cutting down, there are chips flyes off)
#:(для него) это [[тёмный]] лес (''or'' [[дремучий]] лес) ''(saying)'', {{figurative}} — ''it is [[Greek]] (for him)'', ''(he is) completely in the dark about it'' (''literal'': this is the dark forest for him)
#:в лесу́ [[люди]] лесеют, а в людях людеют ''(proverb)'' — ''literal'': ''people become wild in forest, and become people among people''
#:[[чей]] лес, [[тот|того]] и [[пень]] ''(proverb)'' — ''literal'': ''man who owns the forest, owns a stump too''
#:[[Бог]] и ле́су не [[сравнять|сравня́л]] ''(saying)'' - ''literal'': ''God don't even make forest equal'', means that people are not equal
# (only ''singular'') [[lumber]], [[timber]]
#:лес в [[плот|плотах]] (v plotákh) — ''[[timber]] [[float]]''
#:лес на [[корень|корню]] (na kornjú) — ''[[standing]] [[timber]]''
# (only ''plural'') леса́ [[scaffolding]], [[scaffold]] [[trestle]], [[falsework]]
#:леса (lesá) ''pl'' — ''[[scaffolding]], [[scaffold]] [[trestle]]''
# {{figurative}} [[much]], [[many]], [[a lot of]] ''smth.'' (especially high, eminent)
#:лес рук - ''a forest of hands'' (in school if nobody wants to answer teacher's question)
#:лес [[мачта|мачт]] — ''a large number of ships''
#:лес [[штык|штыков]] (štykóv) — ''[[forest]] of [[bayonet]]s''

